From 7e8011b34ad3cd43305370bbfcb0c1943970c773 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Craig Barber <craigb@mojotech.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Mar 2026 23:43:34 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(tui): fetch full message history for export and copy

The TUI message store caps at 100 entries for rendering performance;
/export and /copy were reading from that store, producing truncated
transcripts on compacted or long sessions. Fetch all messages from the
server via a testable helper with no limit.

Authored-By: OpenCode (anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6)
